===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
Modern form is a compound of {{zh-l|*音}} and {{zh-l|*心|heart}}. However, the top component is etymologically unrelated to {{zh-l|*音}}. According to {{zh-ref|Lin (1920)}}, {{zh-l|𠶷}} (a compound of {{zh-l|言*}} and {{zh-l|中*}}) found in bronze inscriptions is the same character as {{zh-l|意}}.

